{
  "stem": "25651.10",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Then one of the-- the men were terribly-- the men in the kleiderkammer were really lucky, because they had access to women, and they were-- they f-- women and men fell on each other when they could get together.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You know, like, tomorrow we die, so we have to have sex.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And these men had-- had access.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they tried to talk me into selecting a girlfriend, and on one of these outings, you know, when we went to sort out clothes, there were 1,000 women, I don't know, from France standing there.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Have you ever seen 1,000 naked women?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's not a very sexy picture.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this [GERMAN], his name was Herting-- I lived with Herting and Nitka in the same-- in a sort of office.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Really privileged quarters we had.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Herting was a Belgian.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they would bring back food, and I would sort of get it-- get it ready in the evening.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Herting always showed me how to make improvised Belgian dishes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Like, for example, I made pancakes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He taught me how to make pancakes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He taught me how to make a fondue with cheeses.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He brought a whole lot of cheeses.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He says, look, the thing to do with these cheeses is to make a fondue.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So, I made a fondue, and he told me exactly what to do.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it was delicious.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, Herting says, look, you can have any of these girls.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And all I have to do is give them some clothes and they'll do anything for you.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I just couldn't-- perhaps I wasn't mature enough.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I just-- I just couldn't.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It, it, it was-- and Nitka goes along and chooses a young girl.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This is something that you were party to.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
